<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <!-- Updated: 2026-03-27 02:18 UTC - Final Feasibility & Technical details -->
  <title>Nouméa Résidences — Surfers Paradise · Gold Coast</title>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Cormorant+Garamond:ital,wght@0,300;0,400;0,600;1,300;1,400&family=Montserrat:wght@200;300;400;500;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />
  <style>
    *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
    :root {
      --gold: #C9A96E;
      --gold-light: #E8D4A8;
      --dark: #080C12;
      --mid: #111720;
      --panel: #181F2C;
      --light: #F8F6F2;
      --muted: #8A8FA0;
      --serif: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
      --sans: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;
    }
    html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }
    body { font-family: var(--sans); background: var(--dark); color: var(--light); overflow-x: hidden; }

    .wrap { max-width: 1240px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 60px; }
    .gold { color: var(--gold); }
    .fade-in { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(28px); transition: opacity 0.8s ease, transform 0.8s ease; }
    .fade-in.visible { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
    .d1 { transition-delay: 0.15s; }
    .d2 { transition-delay: 0.3s; }
    .d3 { transition-delay: 0.45s; }

    /* NAV */
    nav {
      position: fixed; top: 0; left: 0; right: 0; z-index: 999;
      display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center;
      padding: 28px 60px;
      background: linear-gradient(to bottom, rgba(8,12,18,0.97), transparent);
      transition: padding 0.4s, background 0.4s;
    }
    nav.solid { background: rgba(8,12,18,0.97); padding: 18px 60px; box-shadow: 0 1px 0 rgba(201,169,110,0.1); }
    .nav-brand { font-family: var(--serif); font-size: 24px; letter-spacing: 6px; color: var(--gold); text-transform: uppercase; font-weight: 600; }
    .nav-sub { font-size: 9px; letter-spacing: 2px; opacity: 0.4; text-transform: uppercase; margin-top: 2px; }
    .nav-links { display: flex; gap: 32px; list-style: none; }
    .nav-links a { font-size: 11px; letter-spacing: 2px; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--light); opacity: 0.6; text-decoration: none; transition: opacity 0.3s, color 0.3s; }
    .nav-links a:hover { opacity: 1; color: var(--gold); }
    .nav-cta { font-size: 11px; letter-spacing: 2px; text-transform: uppercase; border: 1px solid rgba(201,169,110,0.5); color: var(--gold); padding: 11px 26px; text-decoration: none; transition: background 0.3s; }
    .nav-cta:hover { background: var(--gold); color: var(--dark); border-color: var(--gold); }

    /* HERO */
    .hero { height: 100vh; position: relative; overflow: hidden; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; text-align: center; }
    .hero-bg {
      position: absolute; inset: 0;
      background: url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1510469062325-c6198f8e025a?q=80&w=1920') center bottom/cover no-repeat;
      transform: scale(1.06); transition: transform 10s ease-out;
    }
    .hero-bg.loaded { transform: scale(1); }
    .hero-overlay { position: absolute; inset: 0; background: linear-gradient(to bottom, rgba(8,12,18,0.3) 0%, rgba(8,12,18,0.55) 60%, rgba(8,12,18,0.88) 100%); }
    .hero-content { position: relative; z-index: 2; }
    .hero-eyebrow { font-size: 11px; letter-spacing: 7px; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--gold); margin-bottom: 28px; }
    .hero-title { font-family: var(--serif); font-size: clamp(72px, 10vw, 128px); font-weight: 300; line-height: 0.95; }
    .hero-title em { font-style: italic; color: var(--gold); display: block; }
    .hero-line { width: 1px; height: 56px; background: rgba(201,169,110,0.5); margin: 36px auto; }
    .hero-tagline { font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 7px; text-transform: uppercase; opacity: 0.65; font-weight: 300; }
    .hero-scroll { position: absolute; bottom: 44px; left: 50%; transform: translateX(-50%); display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center; gap: 10px; font-size: 9px; letter-spacing: 3px; text-transform: uppercase; opacity: 0.4; }
    .scroll-line { width: 1px; height: 48px; background: var(--gold); animation: pulse 2s ease-in-out infinite; }
    @keyframes pulse { 0%,100%{opacity:.3;transform:scaleY(1)} 50%{opacity:1;transform:scaleY(.6)} }

    /* STRIP */
    .strip { background: var(--gold); color: var(--dark); padding: 26px 60px; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; gap: 10px; }
    .strip-item { text-align: center; flex: 1; }
    .strip-n { font-family: var(--serif); font-size: 38px; font-weight: 600; line-height: 1; }
    .strip-l { font-size: 9px; letter-spacing: 2px; text-transform: uppercase; opacity: 0.65; margin-top: 6px; }
    .strip-sep { width: 1px; height: 36px; background: rgba(0,0,0,0.15); }

    /* SECTIONS */
    section { padding: 120px 0; }
    .eyebrow { font-size: 10px; letter-spacing: 5px; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--gold); margin-bottom: 18px; }
    .sh { font-family: var(--serif); font-size: clamp(38px, 5vw, 68px); font-weight: 300; line-height: 1.05; margin-bottom: 24px; }
    .body-p { font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.9; opacity: 0.72; }
    .rule { width: 64px; height: 1px; background: var(--gold); margin: 28px 0; }

    /* PROJECT */
    .project-section { background: var(--mid); }
    .proj-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 100px; align-items: center; }
    .proj-img { height: 620px; overflow: hidden; position: relative; }
    .proj-img img { width: 100%; height: 100%; object-fit: cover; }
    .proj-img-cap { position: absolute; bottom: 0; left: 0; right: 0; background: linear-gradient(to top, rgba(8,12,18,.75), transparent); padding: 28px 20px 16px; font-size: 10px; letter-spacing: 2px; text-transform: uppercase; opacity: .7; }
    .pstats { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 32px; margin-top: 52px; }
    .pstat { border-left: 1px solid var(--gold); padding-left: 22px; }
    .pstat-n { font-family: var(--serif); font-size: 46px; font-weight: 300; color: var(--gold); line-height: 1; }
    .pstat-l { font-size: 10px; letter-spacing: 2px; text-transform: uppercase; opacity: .5; margin-top: 8px; }

    /* DIFF */
    .diff-section { background: var(--dark); }
    .diff-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3,1fr); gap: 2px; background: rgba(201,169,110,0.15); margin-top: 64px; }
    .diff-card { background: var(--panel); padding: 48px 40px; }
    .diff-icon { font-size: 30px; margin-bottom: 18px; }
    .diff-title { font-family: var(--serif); font-size: 24px; margin-bottom: 14px; }
    .diff-body { font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.8; opacity: .65; }

    /* GALLERY */
    .gallery-section { padding: 0; }
    .gallery-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 2fr 1fr 1fr; grid-template-rows: 380px 380px; gap: 4px; }
    .gitem { overflow: hidden; position: relative; }
    .gitem img { width: 100%; height: 100%; object-fit: cover; transition: transform .8s ease; display: block; }
    .gitem:hover img { transform: scale(1.06); }
    .gitem.tall { grid-row: span 2; }
    .gcap { position: absolute; bottom: 0; left: 0; right: 0; background: linear-gradient(to top, rgba(8,12,18,.7), transparent); padding: 28px 18px 14px; font-size: 10px; letter-spacing: 2px; text-transform: uppercase; opacity: 0; transition: opacity .3s; }
    .gitem:hover .gcap { opacity: 1; }

    /* HISTORY */
    .history-section { background: var(--panel); }
    .history-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 80px; align-items: center; }
    .history-img { height: 520px; overflow: hidden; }
    .history-img img { width: 100%; height: 100%; object-fit: cover; }
    .timeline { margin-top: 40px; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0; }
    .titem { display: flex; gap: 24px; padding: 20px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(201,169,110,0.1); }
    .titem:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
    .tyear { font-family: var(--serif); font-size: 22px; color: var(--gold); min-width: 60px; line-height: 1.3; }
    .tdesc { font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.75; opacity: .7; }

    /* FEASIBILITY */
    .feas-section { background: var(--dark); }
    .feas-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 40px; margin-top: 64px; }
    .feas-card { border: 1px solid rgba(201,169,110,0.2); background: var(--panel); }
    .feas-card.rec { border-color: var(--gold); }
    .feas-head { padding: 32px 36px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(201,169,110,.1); position: relative; }
    .feas-card.rec .feas-head { background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(201,169,110,.1), transparent); }
    .feas-badge { position: absolute; top: -13px; right: 36px; background: var(--gold); color: var(--dark); font-size: 9px; letter-spacing: 3px; text-transform: uppercase; padding: 4px 16px; font-weight: 700; }
    .feas-sc { font-size: 10px; letter-spacing: 4px; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--gold); margin-bottom: 8px; }
    .feas-nm { font-family: var(--serif); font-size: 28px; font-weight: 300; }
    .feas-body { padding: 28px 36px; }
    .frow { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; padding: 11px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.05); font-size: 14px; }
    .frow:last-child { border: none; }
    .frow .lbl { opacity: .5; }
    .frow .val { font-weight: 500; }
    .feas-tot { background: rgba(201,169,110,.08); padding: 18px 36px; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; }
    .ftlbl { font-size: 10px; letter-spacing: 2px; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--gold); font-weight: 600; }
    .ftval { font-family: var(--serif); font-size: 28px; color: var(--gold); }
    .feas-margin { padding: 20px 36px; background: var(--mid); display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; }
    .feas-card.rec .feas-margin { background: var(--gold); color: var(--dark); }
    .mbig { font-family: var(--serif); font-size: 52px; font-weight: 300; line-height: 1; }
    .msub { font-size: 9px; letter-spacing: 2px; text-transform: uppercase; opacity: .6; margin-top: 4px; }
    .mprofit { text-align: right; }
    .mpn { font-family: var(--serif); font-size: 32px; }
    .mpl { font-size: 9px; letter-spacing: 2px; text-transform: uppercase; opacity: .6; }

    /* COMPARABLES */
    .comp-section { background: var(--mid); }
    .comp-table { margin-top: 56px; border: 1px solid rgba(201,169,110,.15); overflow: hidden; }
    .comp-head { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 2.5fr 1.2fr 1.2fr 1.2fr; padding: 18px 32px; background: rgba(201,169,110,.08); gap: 10px; }
    .comp-hcell { font-size: 10px; letter-spacing: 3px; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--gold); }
    .comp-row { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 2.5fr 1.2fr 1.2fr 1.2fr; padding: 18px 32px; border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.05); gap: 10px; transition: background .2s; }
    .comp-row:hover { background: rgba(201,169,110,.04); }
    .comp-row.noumea { background: rgba(201,169,110,.07); }
    .ccell { font-size: 13px; }
    .ccell.h { color: var(--gold); font-weight: 600; }
    .ccell.g { color: var(--gold); }
    .comp-note { font-size: 12px; opacity: .45; margin-top: 20px; font-style: italic; }

    /* MARKET */
    .market-section { background: var(--dark); }
    .market-grid2 { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 80px; align-items: center; margin-top: 64px; }
    .mkt-img { height: 480px; overflow: hidden; }
    .mkt-img img { width: 100%; height: 100%; object-fit: cover; }
    .mstats { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 28px; }
    .mstat { display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 24px; padding-bottom: 28px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(201,169,110,.1); }
    .mstat:last-child { border: none; padding-bottom: 0; }
    .mstat-n { font-family: var(--serif); font-size: 48px; color: var(--gold); min-width: 130px; line-height: 1; }
    .mstat-l { font-size: 11px; letter-spacing: 1px; font-weight: 500; margin-bottom: 6px; }
    .mstat-d { font-size: 13px; opacity: .6; line-height: 1.7; }

    /* AGENT */
    .agent-section { background: var(--panel); }
    .agent-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1.6fr; gap: 90px; align-items: center; }
    .agent-img-wrap { position: relative; }
    .agent-img { height: 580px; overflow: hidden; }
    .agent-img img { width: 100%; height: 100%; object-fit: cover; object-position: center top; }
    .agent-brand { background: var(--gold); padding: 18px 24px; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 14px; }
    .ngu-name { font-family: var(--serif); font-size: 18px; letter-spacing: 4px; color: var(--dark); font-weight: 700; text-transform: uppercase; }
    .ngu-sub { font-size: 9px; letter-spacing: 2px; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--dark); opacity: .6; }
    .agent-name { font-family: var(--serif); font-size: 56px; font-weight: 300; line-height: 1; margin-bottom: 6px; }
    .agent-title { font-size: 11px; letter-spacing: 3px; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--gold); margin-bottom: 32px; }
    .agent-bio { font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.9; opacity: .72; margin-bottom: 18px; }
    .agent-stats { display: flex; gap: 36px; margin-top: 24px; }
    .astat-n { font-family: var(--serif); font-size: 34px; color: var(--gold); line-height: 1; }
    .astat-l { font-size: 9px; letter-spacing: 2px; text-transform: uppercase; opacity: .45; margin-top: 6px; }
    .agent-btns { display: flex; gap: 16px; margin-top: 40px; flex-wrap: wrap; }
    .abtn { display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px; padding: 14px 30px; border: 1px solid var(--gold); color: var(--gold); text-decoration: none; font-size: 11px; letter-spacing: 2px; text-transform: uppercase; transition: background .3s, color .3s; }
    .abtn:hover, .abtn.solid { background: var(--gold); color: var(--dark); border-color: var(--gold); }
    .abtn.solid:hover { background: var(--gold-light); }

    /* CONTACTS */
    .contacts-section { background: var(--dark); }
    .contacts-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3,1fr); gap: 2px; background: rgba(201,169,110,.1); margin-top: 64px; }
    .ccard { background: var(--panel); padding: 44px 36px; }
    .crole { font-size: 9px; letter-spacing: 5px; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--gold); margin-bottom: 20px; }
    .cname { font-family: var(--serif); font-size: 26px; margin-bottom: 6px; }
    .cfirm { font-size: 12px; opacity: .5; margin-bottom: 24px; }
    .cdetails { font-size: 13px; line-height: 2; opacity: .7; }
    .cdetails a { color: var(--gold); text-decoration: none; }

    /* CONTACT FORM */
    .form-section { background: var(--mid); }
    .form-wrap { max-width: 720px; margin: 0 auto; }
    .form-intro { text-align: center; margin-bottom: 56px; }
    .form-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 20px; }
    .form-full { grid-column: span 2; }
    .form-group { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 8px; }
    .form-group label { font-size: 10px; letter-spacing: 3px; text-transform: uppercase; opacity: .5; }
    .form-group input, .form-group textarea, .form-group select {
      background: rgba(255,255,255,.05); border: 1px solid rgba(201,169,110,.2);
      color: var(--light); padding: 14px 18px; font-family: var(--sans); font-size: 14px;
      outline: none; transition: border-color .3s;
      appearance: none;
    }
    .form-group input:focus, .form-group textarea:focus, .form-group select:focus { border-color: var(--gold); }
    .form-group textarea { height: 140px; resize: vertical; }
    .form-group select option { background: var(--panel); }
    .form-submit {
      display: block; width: 100%; padding: 18px; background: var(--gold); color: var(--dark);
      border: none; font-family: var(--sans); font-size: 12px; letter-spacing: 4px;
      text-transform: uppercase; font-weight: 700; cursor: pointer; margin-top: 12px;
      transition: background .3s;
    }
    .form-submit:hover { background: var(--gold-light); }
    .form-note { font-size: 11px; opacity: .35; text-align: center; margin-top: 16px; }

    /* CTA */
    .cta-section { position: relative; overflow: hidden; text-align: center; padding: 150px 0; }
    .cta-bg { position: absolute; inset: 0; background: url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1527192491265-7e15c55b1ed2?w=1920&q=80') center/cover; filter: brightness(.22); }
    .cta-content { position: relative; z-index: 2; }
    .cta-title { font-family: var(--serif); font-size: clamp(44px, 6vw, 90px); font-weight: 300; margin-bottom: 28px; }
    .cta-body { font-size: 16px; opacity: .65; max-width: 580px; margin: 0 auto 52px; line-height: 1.9; }
    .cta-btn { display: inline-block; padding: 18px 56px; background: var(--gold); color: var(--dark); font-size: 12px; letter-spacing: 4px; text-transform: uppercase; text-decoration: none; font-weight: 700; transition: background .3s; }
    .cta-btn:hover { background: var(--gold-light); }

    /* FOOTER */
    footer { padding: 44px 60px; background: var(--dark); border-top: 1px solid rgba(201,169,110,.1); display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; }
    .fbrand { font-family: var(--serif); font-size: 20px; letter-spacing: 5px; color: var(--gold); text-transform: uppercase; font-weight: 600; }
    .fby { font-size: 10px; letter-spacing: 1px; text-transform: uppercase; opacity: .3; margin-top: 5px; }
    .fnote { font-size: 11px; opacity: .28; text-align: right; line-height: 1.8; }

    /* RESPONSIVE */
    @media (max-width: 1024px) {
      nav, .strip, footer { padding-left: 30px; padding-right: 30px; }
      .wrap { padding: 0 30px; }
      .proj-grid, .market-grid2, .agent-grid, .feas-grid, .history-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .diff-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; }
      .gallery-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; grid-template-rows: auto; }
      .gitem.tall { grid-row: auto; }
      .contacts-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; }
      .form-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .form-full { grid-column: span 1; }
      section { padding: 80px 0; }
    }
    @media (max-width: 680px) {
      nav { padding: 16px 20px; }
      .nav-links { display: none; }
      .wrap { padding: 0 20px; }
      .strip { flex-direction: column; gap: 16px; padding: 28px 20px; }
      .strip-sep { display: none; }
      .diff-grid, .contacts-grid, .feas-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .gallery-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; grid-template-rows: auto; }
      .pstats { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; }
      .comp-head, .comp-row { grid-template-columns: 2fr 1fr 1fr; }
      .comp-hcell:nth-child(4), .ccell:nth-child(4) { display: none; }
      footer { flex-direction: column; gap: 12px; text-align: center; padding: 28px 20px; }
      .fnote { text-align: center; }
    }
    .welcome-overlay { padding-top: 80px; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

<!-- WELCOME OVERLAY -->
<div class="welcome-overlay no-print" id="welcomeOverlay">
  <div class="welcome-content fade-in visible">
    <p class="welcome-eyebrow">Présentation Confidentielle</p>
    <h1 class="welcome-title">Bienvenue<br>M. Daniel Leroux</h1>
    <div class="welcome-line"></div>
    <p class="welcome-subtitle">Explorez les Résidences Nouméa · Surfers Paradise</p>
    <button class="welcome-btn" id="discoverBtn">Découvrir le Projet</button>
  </div>
</div>


<!-- NAV -->
<nav id="nav">
  <div>
    <div class="nav-brand">Nouméa</div>
    <div class="nav-sub">Résidences · Surfers Paradise</div>
  </div>
  <ul class="nav-links">
    <li><a href="#projet">Le Projet</a></li>
    <li><a href="#histoire">Histoire</a></li>
    <li><a href="#faisabilite">Faisabilité</a></li>
    <li><a href="#ventes">Ventes Récentes</a></li>
    <li><a href="#marche">Marché</a></li>
    <li><a href="#contact">Contact</a></li>
  </ul>
  <a href="#contact" class="nav-cta">Nous Contacter</a>
</nav>

<!-- HERO -->
<div class="hero">
  <div class="hero-bg" id="heroBg"></div>
  <div class="hero-overlay"></div>
  <div class="hero-content">
    <p class="hero-eyebrow">Résidences de Prestige · Surfers Paradise</p>
    <h1 class="hero-title">Nouméa<em>Résidences</em></h1>
    <div class="hero-line"></div>
    <p class="hero-tagline">11 Résidences d'Exception · 1 par Étage · Gold Coast, Australie</p>
  </div>
  <div class="hero-scroll"><div class="scroll-line"></div>Découvrir</div>
</div>

<!-- STRIP -->
<div class="strip">
  <div class="strip-item fade-in"><div class="strip-n">11</div><div class="strip-l">Résidences Exclusives</div></div>
  <div class="strip-sep"></div>
  <div class="strip-item fade-in d1"><div class="strip-n">300m²</div><div class="strip-l">Surface par Étage</div></div>
  <div class="strip-sep"></div>
  <div class="strip-item fade-in d2"><div class="strip-n">$3.5–3.8M</div><div class="strip-l">Prix de Vente Cible</div></div>
  <div class="strip-sep"></div>
  <div class="strip-item fade-in d3"><div class="strip-n">29–36%</div><div class="strip-l">Marge Indicative</div></div>
</div>

<!-- PROJECT -->
<section class="project-section" id="projet">
  <div class="wrap proj-grid">
    <div class="proj-img fade-in">
      <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1600596542815-ffad4c1539a9?w=900&q=80" alt="Vue Rivière Nerang" />
      <div class="proj-img-cap">Vue Rivière Nerang · Surfers Paradise</div>
    </div>
    <div class="fade-in d1">
      <p class="eyebrow">Le Projet</p>
      <h2 class="sh">Une Vision d'Excellence<br><em class="gold" style="font-family:var(--serif)">au Bord du Fleuve</em></h2>
      <div class="rule"></div>
      <p class="body-p">Nouméa Résidences est un projet immobilier de prestige en première ligne de la rivière Nerang à Surfers Paradise. <strong>11 niveaux. 11 résidences. Une seule par étage</strong> — exclusivité absolue et intimité totale.</p>
      <p class="body-p" style="margin-top:18px;">Chaque résidence plein étage de 300 m² dispose de 1.5 places de stationnement dédiées, d'un accès privatif depuis l'ascenseur et de vues panoramiques sur la rivière et la skyline de la Gold Coast.</p>
      <p class="body-p" style="margin-top:18px;">Conçu pour une clientèle internationale exigeante, ce projet conjugue architecture contemporaine, finitions haut de gamme et positionnement stratégique exceptionnel.</p>
      <div class="pstats">
        <div class="pstat"><div class="pstat-n">11</div><div class="pstat-l">Résidences Exclusives</div></div>
        <div class="pstat"><div class="pstat-n">300<span style="font-size:22px">m²</span></div><div class="pstat-l">Surface par Étage</div></div>
        <div class="pstat"><div class="pstat-n">1.5</div><div class="pstat-l">Parkings / Appartement</div></div>
        <div class="pstat"><div class="pstat-n">2032</div><div class="pstat-l">JO Brisbane</div></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- DIFFERENTIATORS -->
<section class="diff-section">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="fade-in" style="text-align:center;">
      <p class="eyebrow" style="text-align:center;">Pourquoi Nouméa</p>
      <h2 class="sh" style="text-align:center;">Ce Qui Rend ce Projet <span class="gold">Unique</span></h2>
    </div>
    <div class="diff-grid fade-in d1">
      <div class="diff-card"><div class="diff-icon">🏢</div><div class="diff-title">1 Résidence par Étage</div><div class="diff-body">L'exclusivité absolue. Chaque résident possède l'intégralité de son niveau — pas de voisins de palier, une intimité totale, des vues non obstruées à 270°.</div></div>
      <div class="diff-card"><div class="diff-icon">🌊</div><div class="diff-title">Première Ligne Rivière</div><div class="diff-body">Une localisation riveraine de premier rang sur la Nerang à Surfers Paradise — l'un des corridors les plus prisés et les plus rares de la Gold Coast premium.</div></div>
      <div class="diff-card"><div class="diff-icon">🏅</div><div class="diff-title">Brisbane 2032</div><div class="diff-body">La Gold Coast bénéficiera directement des Jeux Olympiques de Brisbane 2032 — infrastructures, visibilité mondiale et valorisation accélérée.</div></div>
      <div class="diff-card"><div class="diff-icon">🌏</div><div class="diff-title">Acheteurs Internationaux</div><div class="diff-body">Des acheteurs fortunés d'Europe, d'Asie et du Pacifique ciblent activement la Gold Coast pour des actifs lifestyle premium. Marché en pleine expansion.</div></div>
      <div class="diff-card"><div class="diff-icon">📐</div><div class="diff-title">300m² · Rare sur le Marché</div><div class="diff-body">300 m² plein étage est un format quasi introuvable à ce prix sur la Gold Coast. La rareté crée une valeur intrinsèque durable et protège l'investissement.</div></div>
      <div class="diff-card"><div class="diff-icon">📈</div><div class="diff-title">Positionnement Stratégique</div><div class="diff-body">À un prix de vente moyen cible de $3.5M–$3.95M pour 300 m², le projet se positionne à ~$11 700–$13 167/m² — bien en dessous des comparables plein étage ($17 000–$26 000/m²). Une marge de hausse réelle avec un risque contenu.</div></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

